Class GateWay

java.lang.Object
java.rmi.server.RemoteObject
java.rmi.server.RemoteServer
java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
sd_projeto.GateWay
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Remote, Request
public class GateWay extends UnicastRemoteObject implements Request
Classe que representa o Gateway do motor de busca. O Gateway coordena as solicitações entre o cliente e os barrels ou a queue.
